# Dart build/cache artifacts. pubspec.lock IS committed (the authoritative,
# reproducible dependency set for `dart pub get --offline`).
#
# bin/ is the IDIOMATIC Dart source location for the host entrypoint
# (profile [layout].bin_dir = "bin/"; bin/peer.dart is the S4 AOT host SOURCE,
# not a compiled artifact). The meta-repo root .gitignore has a broad `**/bin/`
# rule (for compiled binary dirs); un-ignore this package's source bin/ so the
# host entrypoint is tracked. The AOT-compiled exe is produced at S4 build time
# into the image / a build dir, not committed.
!bin/
!bin/*.dart
.dart_tool/
.packages
build/
build-s4/
doc/api/
*.js
*.js.map
*.js.deps
.web_smoke_out.js
